The mode of the inefficiency score is obtained by maximizing the distribution 
of $u_i|\epsilon_i$, and solving the following equation:

$$\frac{\partial f(u_i|\epsilon_i)}{\partial u_i} = 0$$

which yields $-S\epsilon$. When $-\theta < S\epsilon < 0$, the mode is 
